menu "CSI Transmitter Configuration"

config CSI_TX_CHANNEL
    int "WiFi channel (ESP-NOW)"
    range 1 13
    default 11
    help
        Both transmitter and receiver must be on the same channel.
        Channel 11 typically has the least interference in the 2.4 GHz band.

config CSI_TX_RATE_HZ
    int "Broadcast rate (Hz)"
    range 1 500
    default 100
    help
        How often we broadcast an ESP-NOW packet. Each broadcast triggers one
        CSI sample on every receiver, so this is the effective sample rate.

endmenu
